Heleq sheni : me-hamishah humshe Torah : al-pi diqduq we-'iyun gadol ke-nizkar ba-sha'ar heleq ha-ri'shon im ha-'asarah shelitim 'asher be ... kol asher helqo heleq mishmetu mishmat 'eleh mishe'al 'asher qiblah me-har Sinai im ha-megilot ve-ha-haftarot ha-nikra'im bi-zmanehem ba-'asher 'ineikhem tehazne mi-yesharim

Sefer Tsahut ba-diqduq / she-hibber he-khakham ha-gadol R. Abraham ben Meir ha-sefaradi z''al ha-mekhune ben Ezra midpas bi-shnat hameshet alafim we-shalosh meot we-shisha la-yetsira. be-Venezia. We-ata huatak shenit, meuleh min ha-rishonit be-hagaah iyunit, hinne edah ha-tavnit, u-psukei mikraot, rubbam me-ha-nimtsaot, asher le-mofet muvaot, mehubbarim be-lulaot. Yimtsam ha-kore bli leut, be-hotsaot ha-bakhurim [he hakham ha-gadol] ha-bakhur [kevod harav rabbí] Reuben Arenswald we-ha-bakhur [kevod ha-rav rabbí] Aharon Yerslov we-gam hoge al-yado
